text: Devereaux Jennings (June 28, 1924 - April 14, 2000) was an American alpine skier. He competed in the men's downhill at the 1948 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1924 births Category:2000 deaths Category:American male alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of the United States Category:Alpine skiers at the 1948 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Salt Lake City
